title: United Kingdom Imports of Meat & Edible Meat Offal
description: Imports of Meat & Edible Meat Offal in the United Kingdom increased to 374.21 GBP Million in September from 370.21 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Meat & Edible Meat Offal in the United Kingdom averaged 282.75 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 428.88 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 71.28 GBP Million in February of 2022. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Meat & Edible Meat Offal.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
